# health-back rules

- Source of truth is TypeScript in `src/**/*.ts`. Don’t add/edit compiled JS in `dist/`.
- Prisma workflow:
  - schema changes go in `prisma/schema.prisma`
  - apply via `npm run prisma:migrate`
  - run `npm run prisma:generate` after schema updates
- Auth:
  - protected routes must use `requireAuth`
  - super-admin-only routes must use `requireSuperAdmin` (403 if not allowed)
- When adding new endpoints, keep response shape stable and update `health-front` proxy routes when needed.

